{
  "stem": "16214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's only my grandparents, actually-- my other grandparents-- were living in Kraszkow-- in Kraszkow, in the town-- village where my mother left me.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And basically, when my mother came after the war, she went straight away right after-- she went straight to the-- the little village where she left me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in Kraszkow, she had that little picture, which I showed you previously.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the only thing she had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she came over to one of the village-- there was a pasture, I believe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sheep were on that pasture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother went over to the shepherdess and asked her, did you-- by any chance, do you know a little girl who was left here back in 1942?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you remember her, or do you know where she is?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the lady-- the old lady said, oh, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Romeskza-- ?] that's a diminutive of Romana, which is my name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was-- she looked at the picture which my mother showed her and she says, yes, that's [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Romeskza. ?] She doesn't live here anymore, but her grandma is here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how my mother was able to go and see my grandma for the first time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And through her, she-- she found out where I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know personally of what actually-- what did he do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know that he certainly was anti-semite in order to belong to that organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but he had no-- he was-- he was really-- other than-- you know, it's-- it's just incredible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he was a very loving man-- very very nice person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so was the lady who, you know-- his wife.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
